name: Ensaymada
description: Our most popular and beloved item. The Ensaymada is a luxurious Filipino brioche, famously soft, rich, and buttery, topped with creamy butter and a generous sprinkle of sugar and cheese, offering a unique blend of sweet and savory flavors.

name: Chocolate Crinkle Cookies
description: Savor the rich, chocolatey delight of our Chocolate Crinkle Cookies, dusted with powdered sugar for a perfect sweet and cocoa balance.

name: Red Velvet Cupcakes
description: Indulge in our elegant Red Velvet Cupcakes, offering that unique 'Red Velvet' flavor paired with creamy cheese frosting for a luxurious treat.

name: Chocolate Cake
description: Delight in our Chocolate Cake, a layered sensation of moist sponge and smooth ganache, offering a deeply satisfying chocolate experience.

name: Walnut & Chocolate Chip Banana Cake
description: Enjoy the comforting blend of our Walnut & Chocolate Chip Banana Cake, a perfect mix of nutty crunch and sweet chocolate in every slice.
